text.textblock: The plat, in one sheet, of a portion of George Washington Memorial Parkway, Fairfax County, Virginia, has been officially filed in Eastern States, Springfield, Virginia, at 7:30 a.m., on December 17, 1993.
The survey was made upon request submitted by the National Park Service.
Copies of the plat will be made available upon request and prepayment of the reproduction fee of $4.00 per copy.

doctitle.textblock: Notice of Filing of Plat of Dependent Resurvey
